    	        <h3>Cloud Computing and Synergy Chat</h3>
               Cloud Computing is a relatively new term for internet users. The concept of cloud computing is relatively simple: Instead of running programs and storing information on your desktop you instead run programs and store information directly on the internet using only your browser. There are many advantages to cloud computing: Local servers are not needed, valuable information is stored securely offsite, and best of all you can access the cloud from anywhere on any computer with internet access. The technological advantages provide a more efficient, productive and cost effective method of computing. Synergy Chat utilizes the cloud in a very unique way:
