With Synergy Chat it is extremely easy to video chat face to face. When a Synergy Chat member is logged into the member interface they can easily chat with other members from their group as well as guests. A Synergy Chat member simply clicks on another member&#39;s name on the member list or clicks on a guest name from the guest waiting list. Once a video chat is initiated you can chat as long as you wish. There is also the option to type using the text chat window. A webcam is not required in order to conduct a video chat. Anyone can use the audio signal to verbally communicate or use just the text chat box.
