SynergyChat also offers the ability to video conference with up to nine people at the same time. Only one Synergy Chat member is required in order to schedule a video conference. Up to eight guests may join the video conference. The Synergy Chat member clicks create conference, enters all attendees email adresses, titles the conference, selected the date and time, and then clicks create. Once the conference is created every attendee with recieve an email with the conference information as well as a link to enter the conference. Once inside of the video conference all attendees can hear each other simultaneously.
