Every Synergy Chat member can easily record a video email to send to anyone they wish.  The video message is stored on the cloud and does not require the recipient to download anything. They simply click the link in the email and are directed to our servers for playback. Recording a video email is easy. Click on the envelope icon, click record, click stop, save the video, click send and enter the email addresses of the people you wish to have view the video message. You can also see your saved video messages by clicking on the View Video Mail tab. It is all that easy!
